===Verb===
'''to float'''

#To have a [[solid]] object, or a different [[liquid]] sit on top of a liquid of greater density.
#To have a lighter-than-air object (balloon) drift through the air.
#To have an object's position be automatically adjusted as parameters of the object or other objects around it change.

