*[[Dutch]]: [[drijven]]
*[[French]]: [[flotter]]

===Noun===
'''float'''

#A [[buoyant]] device used to support something in water or another liquid.
#A sort of [[trowel]] used for finishing [[concrete]] surfaces.
#An elaborately decorated trailer or vehicle, intended for display in a parade or pagent.
#The amount of committed funds (eg, checks written) for a bank account that has not yet cleared a bank and been charged against the account.

